現任總主教為{{link-it|保祿·朱列蒂|Paolo Giulietti}}，榮休總主教為{{link-it|本凡諾多·伊塔洛·卡斯泰拉尼|Benvenuto Italo Castellani}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 19.01.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/01/19/0046/00100.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715081123/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/01/19/0046/00100.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=it |date=2019-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

